text.tspan: Imported or exported CO₂ emissions per capita
This measures the net import-export balance in tonnes of CO₂ per capita.
Positive values (red) show net importers of CO₂. Negative values (blue) show net exporters of CO₂.
Data source: Global Carbon Budget (2022); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (Systema Globalis)
